{"tid":608673,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人好嚮往讀緊大學嘅日子","createTime":"2018-03-28T10:51:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-28T13:23:42.000Z","uid":114633,"like":35,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"bd6f25ef7e9b66b31b115e5b0596c03fb7423efa","tid":608673,"uid":114633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T10:51:31.000Z","msg":"日日走堂 瞓醒就搵fd周圍fing<br />\n晏晝食個T 夜晚就成班出嚟食飯<br />\n飲酒打機第朝有又走堂<br />\n假期又多 一有時間就去旅行<br />\n試過貪機票平<br />\n特登開咗學成個禮拜冇返去旅行<br />\n<br />\n明明就一個垃圾廢青<br />\n大時大節 一同D親戚講自己讀邊間<br />\n個個都讚話幾好呀 叻仔喎<br />\n話父母第時唔使擔心<br />\n<br />\n試過搭幾次的士返hall<br />\n都可以俾個的士司機讚話間學校好難入<br />\n<br />\n其實我知道勁過我嘅人大有人在<br />\n我亦都唔係想話自己好勁<br />\n只不過我真係好享受依種<br />\n明明日日都無所事事嘅日子<br />\n但係都會係咁俾人讚嘅感覺 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申三大 year2 仲有兩年Fing"},{"pid":"e4ae5c1d0fd04c5046c2ad1969f01ecb2c0897b5","tid":608673,"uid":114633,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T10:56:01.000Z","msg":"有無人有同感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3f508a936acc2f94dbe9faac126234e99de27c2","tid":608673,"uid":38461,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T10:57:05.000Z","msg":"有 晚晚打機winning 第二朝訓到晏晝去食個tea<br />\n仲有flirt吓女 飲下酒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca0172f21bda760748b90b93ce0c52aaf7f7113c","tid":608673,"uid":59192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T10:57:45.000Z","msg":"巴打平時洗費邊度黎"},{"pid":"7b92eb68bcee649847e69fe1ae5350753d7322f7","tid":608673,"uid":114633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c3f508a936acc2f94dbe9faac126234e99de27c2","tid":608673,"uid":38461,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T10:57:05.000Z","msg":"有 晚晚打機winning 第二朝訓到晏晝去食個tea<br />\n仲有flirt吓女 飲下酒<img src=\"/assets/faces/